# Cursor indexes fewer files — faster context and lower token use.
# Uses .gitignore-style patterns.

# Build outputs (large, regenerated constantly)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish/
**/out/
**/artifacts/

# Visual Studio / IDE caches
.vs/
.idea/

# NuGet package caches inside the repo
**/packages/

# Test & coverage outputs
**/TestResults/
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Installer / release artifacts (large binaries)
installer/output/

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
